CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

September 17, 2010

[Cite as 09H7/2010 Case Announcements #2, 2010-Ohio-4396.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2010-1636. State v. Gunnell.

Clark App. No. 09CA0013. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution of the court of appeals’ judgment,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.

Pfeifer, J., dissents.
